description:
Pastor Wilson has a special message of hope and love to share this week. Building on the foundation of believers through the ages who spoke the truth of Scripture boldly, he shares truth pertinent to the time at hand. The message: One of the most obvious attacks today is regarding human sexuality, where God's Word is turned on its head and interpreted the opposite of what is written. 

Some of the most basic facts given in Scripture are being ignored or twisted, such as Genesis 1:27 and 28 which say, "So God created man in His own image; in the image of God He created him; male and female He created them. Then God blessed them, and . . . said to them, 'Be fruitful and multiply. . .'"

To learn more about human sexuality and how it relates to our present experience, subscribe to our channel for updates.
fulltitle: Taking a Bold Stand on Human Sexuality: A Special Message from Pastor Ted Wilson
